{"success":true,"message":"操作成功","code":200,"subCode":"","result":{"id":"172","name":"地理编码","path":null,"personDayQuato":null,"enterpriseDayQuato":null,"personMinQuato":null,"enterpriseMinQuato":null,"personMonthQuato":null,"enterpriseMonthQuato":null,"personSumQuato":null,"enterpriseSumQuato":null,"code":null,"certificationNeeded":null,"description":null,"owner":null,"firstType":0,"serviceType":1,"secondType":null,"status":2,"requestType":0,"special":0,"applicationType":0,"innerUrl":null,"outerUrl":null,"wordContext":"# 地理编码\n\n## 接口说明\n\n用户可通过该功能，将结构化地址（省/市/区/街道/门牌号）解析为对应的位置坐标。地址结构越完整，地址内容越准确，解析的坐标精度越高。\n\n## API服务地址\n\n``````\n生产环境：https://gis-apis.sf-express.com/all/api/geocode/geo\n请求方式：get/post\n``````\n\n## 请求参数\n<table>\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th style=\"min-width:100px;\">参数名称</th>\n            <th>参数含义</th>\n            <th style=\"min-width:100px;\">示例</th>\n            <th style=\"width:80px;\">类型</th>\n            <th style=\"width:70px;\">必需</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td>address</td>\n            <td>待解析的地址</td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>是</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>city</td>\n            <td>地址所在城市，可以是城市中文名，可以是420100、755。如果city不为空，则首先以city的内容为准，否则从address中获取城市，如果city和address里面的城市都为空则会返回标准的“空记录（格式请见详细说明）”</td>\n            <td>深圳市</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>否</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>cc</td>\n            <td>坐标系，默认为1 <br> 1-高德坐标系 <br> 2-bd经纬度坐标</td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td>number</td>\n            <td>否</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>ak</td>\n            <td>用户申请的授权码，<span style=\"color:red\">需放到header中</span></td>\n            <td>无</td>\n            <td>string</td>\n            <td>是</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n请求示例\n``````json\n{\n    \"address\": \"深圳市软件产业基地\"\n}\n``````\n\n## 返回参数\n\n<table>\n    <thead>\n       <tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>src</td>\n    <td>\n        来源\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>type</td>\n    <td>\n        地址类型\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>precision</td>\n    <td>\n        精准度\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>xcoord</td>\n    <td>\n        经度（示例：116.403874）\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>ycoord</td>\n    <td>\n        纬度（示例：39.914885）\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>adcode</td>\n    <td>\n        行政区划代码（示例：440300）\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>adname</td>\n    <td>\n        区划名称（示例：深圳市）\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>confidence</td>\n    <td>\n        置信度标记\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>source</td>\n    <td>\n        匹配来源\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>cp</td>\n    <td>\n        匹配标记\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>standardization</td>\n    <td>\n        标准地址\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>time</td>\n    <td>\n        时间（示例：2026-01-07 10:00:00）\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>match_level</td>\n    <td>\n        匹配等级\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>geo_source</td>\n    <td>\n        数据来源\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>src_level</td>\n    <td>\n        地址等级\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>src_level_desc</td>\n    <td>\n        地址等级描述\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>geo_level</td>\n    <td>\n        匹配等级\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>geo_level_desc</td>\n    <td>\n        匹配等级描述\n    </td>\n    <td>string</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>